headline: Oregon, New Hampshire, Ohio and Hawai’i lawmakers consider landfill restrictions
summary: Bills meant to restrict landfill expansions or operations are awaiting governors’ approval in several states, while New Hampshire lawmakers are mulling landfill siting provisions in a recent budget bill.
